this restaurant must be good.

493
00:33:36,483 --> 00:33:37,763
Does it good?

494
00:33:37,763 --> 00:33:38,803
Senior, does it good?

495
00:33:39,523 --> 00:33:40,128
Yes.

496
00:33:41,123 --> 00:33:43,803
