I'll have some juice.

504
00:34:06,443 --> 00:34:07,643
Sure, orange juice?

505
00:34:07,643 --> 00:34:08,443
Sure.

506
00:34:08,443 --> 00:34:09,843
Senior, we'd drink.

507
00:34:10,803 --> 00:34:12,202
I have to drive.

508
00:34:12,202 --> 00:34:16,123
